{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-19", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "直指命運", "storyInfo": "阿勒黛·坎伯蘭，終有一日，你會與維娜再次相逢。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g9_kingrest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_5_7_shining", "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_stmkgt_h", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噴氣聲。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉悶的噴氣聲。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“**，快站起來。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“該去訓練了，**。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“真有你的啊，**，這麼年輕就當上了蒸汽騎士！你是我們的驕傲，是維多利亞的驕傲！”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾個模糊的音節。是誰在呼喚他的姓名嗎？"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可他已經不記得自己到底叫什麼了。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“埃文斯”“瓊斯”“威爾遜”，還是“林奇”？"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他誰都不是，又彷彿誰都是。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我們是蒸汽騎士。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我們誓死守衛維多利亞。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是為什麼......"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼在砍向他們的異族的刀劍之後，藏匿著同胞的身影？"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰友們逐一倒下。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後只剩下他一個。他是......最後的蒸汽騎士。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不能再倒下。他倒下了，蒸汽騎士就倒下了。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞仍需要他，他必須履行自己的職責。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有醫藥，沒關係，盔甲會填補他的血肉。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有食物，沒關係，黑暗之中總有一些窸窸窣窣的小動物爬過。"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有照明，沒關係，那把劍能帶給他唯一的光輝。"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還沒有死。蒸汽騎士沒有死。他們依然在守護維多利亞。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而......"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼是維多利亞？"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我向國王宣誓，向人民許諾，向大地致敬。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我堅守過無數漫長黑夜，卻不知該往何處尋找一生效忠的屬於維多利亞的光明。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞是國王嗎？"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "國王被吊死了。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞是議會與貴族們嗎？"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有維護，沒有補給，沒有新加入的成員，他們一次次將蒸汽騎士派去必死的險境，為他們的貪婪摘取果實。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞是民眾嗎？"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "民眾傳頌著蒸汽騎士，崇拜著蒸汽騎士，卻也將自己所有的渴求寄託在了蒸汽騎士之上。沒有什麼能承載如此矛盾，如此龐雜的希望。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞是什麼？"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞是不是只是一種想像？"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好在，還有這把劍，諸王之息。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無可辯駁，它就是維多利亞的象徵。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，蒸汽騎士認定，那麼現在，它就是自己的維多利亞。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，有人想要玷污他的維多利亞。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他無法容忍。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不能失去自己最後的——"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 6